summary:
The Security Council,

1. Decides that:
(a) Judge Dolenc finish the Cyangugu case before expiry of his term;
(b) Judge Maqutu finish the Kajelijeli and Kamuhanda cases before expiry of his term;
(c) Notwithstanding Article 11, paragraph 1, of the Tribunal's Statute, Judge Ostrovsky finish the Cyangugu case before expiry of his term;
(d) Judge Pillay finish the Media case before expiry of her term;

2. Takes note of the Tribunal's intention to finish the Cyangugu case by February 2004 and the Kajelijeli, Kamuhanda, and Media cases by December 2003;

3. Requests the President of the Tribunal to provide progress reports by: 
- 1 August 2003 
- 15 November 2003 
- 15 January 2004.
